data.description: For sale: A charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom family home in the heart of Palm Bay, Florida. This inviting residence features a spacious kitchen with modern appliances and an adjacent screened-in patio, ideal for outdoor enjoyment. The four bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. The large backyard, with dedicated trailer parking, is perfect for outdoor activities. Located in the vibrant community of Palm Bay, this home provides easy access to parks, restaurants, shopping, and excellent schools. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this your cherished home.
